snippet.title: Johnny Depp Granted Amber Heard's Phone Records
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's legal team has been granted access to Amber Heard's phone. According to court documents filed in Virginia this week, Depp's attorneys reportedly claim that forensic assessment will prove that photos Heard previously used as alleged proof that Depp abused her were manipulated. In response, Heard's attorneys reportedly said she "remains willing and able to support the authenticity of her evidence." Access Hollywood has reached out to Depp and Heard's respective reps for comment.
